::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code  code-line-numbers="false"}
## subset by name (still a list)
x_lst["idx"]  
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
$idx
[1] 1 2 3
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code  code-line-numbers="false"}
## subset by indexing (still a list)
