[2,]    2    5
[3,]    3    6
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code  code-line-numbers="false"}
mat_c <- matrix(data = c(7,0,0,8,2,6), 
                nrow = 3, ncol = 2)
## should have the same number of rows
cbind(mat, mat_c)  
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
     [,1] [,2] [,3] [,4]
