::: notes

- **p-th percentile**: a data value such that at most $p\%$ of the data values are below it and at most $(1âˆ’p)\%$ of the values are above it.
- **First Quartile (Q1)**: the 25-th percentile
- **Second Quartile (Q2)**: the 50-th percentile (Median)
- **Third Quartile (Q3)**: the 75-th percentile
- **Interquartile Range (IQR)**: Q3 - Q1

IQR(data)

::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

